"use strict";(self.webpackChunkwangdoc=self.webpackChunkwangdoc||[]).push([[4630],{79225:(n,s,a)=>{a.r(s),a.d(s,{data:()=>e});const e={key:"v-67b8dbdd",path:"/node-tutorial/promise.html",title:"Promise",lang:"zh-CN",frontmatter:{summary:"Promise UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning 如果 Promise 运行过程中抛出错误，或者状态变为rejected，但是没有相应的处理代码，那么 Node 会抛出一个警告UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning。 上面代码中，Promise 变为rejected状态，但是没有处理的代码，导致抛出警",head:[["meta",{property:"og:url",content:"https://yzqbooks.github.io/wangdoc/wangdoc/node-tutorial/promise.html"}],["meta",{property:"og:site_name",content:"wangdoc"}],["meta",{property:"og:title",content:"Promise"}],["meta",{property:"og:type",content:"article"}],["meta",{property:"og:updated_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}],["meta",{property:"og:locale",content:"zh-CN"}],["meta",{property:"article:modified_time",content:"2022-04-06T10:09:00.000Z"}]]},excerpt:"",headers:[{level:2,title:"UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning",slug:"unhandledpromiserejectionwarning",children:[]}],git:{createdTime:164923974e4,updatedTime:164923974e4,contributors:[{name:"yzqdev",email:"yzqdev@outlook.com",commits:1}]},readingTime:{minutes:1.53,words:459},filePathRelative:"node-tutorial/promise.md"}},72187:(n,s,a)=>{a.r(s),a.d(s,{default:()=>t});const e=(0,a(66252).uE)('<h1 id="promise" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#promise" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Promise</h1><h2 id="unhandledpromiserejectionwarning" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#unhandledpromiserejectionwarning" aria-hidden="true">#</a> UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</h2><p>如果 Promise 运行过程中抛出错误，或者状态变为<code>rejected</code>，但是没有相应的处理代码，那么 Node 会抛出一个警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>。</p><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Promise</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">resolve<span class="token punctuation">,</span> reject</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token function">reject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;message&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>\n<span class="token comment">// hello</span>\n<span class="token comment">// UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning: message</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div><p>上面代码中，Promise 变为<code>rejected</code>状态，但是没有处理的代码，导致抛出警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>。由于抛出的是警告，而不是错误，所以不影响<code>hello</code>的输出。请跟下面的代码比较一下。</p><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Promise</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">resolve<span class="token punctuation">,</span> reject</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token keyword">throw</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Error</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;message&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>\n<span class="token comment">// UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning: Error: message</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br></div></div><p>上面代码中，Promise 内部抛出错误，没有得到处理，所以会有警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>。Promise 内部的错误阻止 Promise 内部的代码继续向下运行，所以不会输出<code>hello</code>。</p><p>消除这个警告的方法很简单，就是为 Promise 加上错误处理代码，即<code>catch</code>代码块。</p><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Promise</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">resolve<span class="token punctuation">,</span> reject</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token function">reject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;message&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">catch</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">err</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span> console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>\n<span class="token comment">// hello</span>\n<span class="token comment">// message</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br></div></div><p>上面代码中，由于<code>catch</code>代码块的存在，所以不会抛出警告。</p><p>async 函数里面使用 Promise，也要放在<code>try/catch</code>代码块之中。</p><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">const</span> p <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Promise</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">resolve<span class="token punctuation">,</span> reject</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token function">reject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;message&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n\n<span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">async</span> <span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token keyword">try</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n    <span class="token keyword">await</span> p<span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  <span class="token punctuation">}</span> <span class="token keyword">catch</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n    console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n  <span class="token punctuation">}</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token comment">// message</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br><span class="line-number">9</span><br><span class="line-number">10</span><br><span class="line-number">11</span><br><span class="line-number">12</span><br></div></div><p>上面代码中，如果 Promise 没有放在<code>try/catch</code>代码块，就会抛出警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>。</p><p>Node 还提供<code>process</code>对象的<code>unhandledRejection</code>事件，在抛出警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>之前，就会触发这个事件。如果设置了这个事件的处理代码，就不会抛出警告<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>。</p><div class="language-javascript ext-js line-numbers-mode"><pre class="language-javascript"><code><span class="token keyword">new</span> <span class="token class-name">Promise</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">resolve<span class="token punctuation">,</span> reject</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  <span class="token function">reject</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;message&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n\nprocess<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">on</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">&#39;unhandledRejection&#39;</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">function</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token parameter">err</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token punctuation">{</span>\n  console<span class="token punctuation">.</span><span class="token function">log</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span>err<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n<span class="token comment">// message</span>\n</code></pre><div class="line-numbers" aria-hidden="true"><span class="line-number">1</span><br><span class="line-number">2</span><br><span class="line-number">3</span><br><span class="line-number">4</span><br><span class="line-number">5</span><br><span class="line-number">6</span><br><span class="line-number">7</span><br><span class="line-number">8</span><br></div></div><p>Node 开发团队打算废除<code>UnhandledPromiseRejectionWarning</code>，以后如果没有相应的处理代码，Promise 内部抛错或者变为<code>rejected</code>状态，会导致 Node 进程终止执行，并且有一个非零的返回码。所以应该养成习惯，只要有 Promise，就要部署失败情况下的代码。</p>',16),p={},t=(0,a(83744).Z)(p,[["render",function(n,s){return e}]])},83744:(n,s)=>{s.Z=(n,s)=>{const a=n.__vccOpts||n;for(const[n,e]of s)a[n]=e;return a}}}]);